custom/handlers.rb and custom/commands.rb are reloaded on each message if the files exist.

Example commands.rb:

    class Rubino::Commands
      def set_custom
        command :ping do
          reply "pong"
        end
      end
    end


Example handlers.rb:

    class Rubino::Handlers
      def set_custom
        on :invite do
          join last.text
        end
      end
    end

More information available at http://duckinator.net/rubino
